  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blow it up is a physics destruction game with light-puzzle elements where you shoot bombs to destroy your enemies who are hiding behind tower-like structures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master seven unique bombs in a realistic physics simulation and explore over 70 levels of mayhem and destruction. With Steamworks integration, you can play custom levels or unleash your creativity in Creator Mode to build your own explosive puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/285f5a1bf03a8bae135f61a959f1160a.poster.avif?t=1739894795\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/285f5a1bf03a8bae135f61a959f1160a.webm?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/285f5a1bf03a8bae135f61a959f1160a.mp4?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORYLINE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An alien invasion is in full swing—mysterious, powerful creatures have descended upon BOOMTOPIA, stripping it of its natural resources and claiming dominance with their explosive superpowers. As your friends are captured one by one, you’ve had enough. Fueled by determination, you gear up to fight back. The adventure begins, but with chaos all around, can you truly survive the mayhem and rescue all your friends?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect Shot! Aim your bomb at the right spot and watch everything collapse!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/6d8d9319ccc546cba26eadf5c6f30e28.poster.avif?t=1739894795\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/6d8d9319ccc546cba26eadf5c6f30e28.webm?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/6d8d9319ccc546cba26eadf5c6f30e28.mp4?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for your imprisoned friends and rescue them one by one!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/0b8ddcf7151a7fed3145675aab1545b5.poster.avif?t=1739894795\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/0b8ddcf7151a7fed3145675aab1545b5.webm?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/0b8ddcf7151a7fed3145675aab1545b5.mp4?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a pure physics-destruction experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/85838192f81ed3133cc623f56e890406.poster.avif?t=1739894795\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/85838192f81ed3133cc623f56e890406.webm?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/85838192f81ed3133cc623f56e890406.mp4?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 unique bombs to destroy your enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advanced <strong>physics simulation</strong> where every block behaves naturally.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a world</strong> of adventure and rescue your friends!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 70 levels of mayhem and destruction.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TNT, confetti and fireworks for more spectacular explosions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steamworks</strong> integration to share and play creations from other players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Creator Mode</strong> where you can build your own levels!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blow it up is the ultimate explosive experience!!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blow it up is a physics destruction game with light-puzzle elements where you shoot bombs to destroy your enemies who are hiding behind tower-like structures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master seven unique bombs in a realistic physics simulation and explore over 70 levels of mayhem and destruction. With Steamworks integration, you can play custom levels or unleash your creativity in Creator Mode to build your own explosive puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/285f5a1bf03a8bae135f61a959f1160a.poster.avif?t=1739894795\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/285f5a1bf03a8bae135f61a959f1160a.webm?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/285f5a1bf03a8bae135f61a959f1160a.mp4?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORYLINE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An alien invasion is in full swing—mysterious, powerful creatures have descended upon BOOMTOPIA, stripping it of its natural resources and claiming dominance with their explosive superpowers. As your friends are captured one by one, you’ve had enough. Fueled by determination, you gear up to fight back. The adventure begins, but with chaos all around, can you truly survive the mayhem and rescue all your friends?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect Shot! Aim your bomb at the right spot and watch everything collapse!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/6d8d9319ccc546cba26eadf5c6f30e28.poster.avif?t=1739894795\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/6d8d9319ccc546cba26eadf5c6f30e28.webm?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/6d8d9319ccc546cba26eadf5c6f30e28.mp4?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for your imprisoned friends and rescue them one by one!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/0b8ddcf7151a7fed3145675aab1545b5.poster.avif?t=1739894795\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/0b8ddcf7151a7fed3145675aab1545b5.webm?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/0b8ddcf7151a7fed3145675aab1545b5.mp4?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a pure physics-destruction experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/85838192f81ed3133cc623f56e890406.poster.avif?t=1739894795\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/85838192f81ed3133cc623f56e890406.webm?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309460/extras/85838192f81ed3133cc623f56e890406.mp4?t=1739894795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 unique bombs to destroy your enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advanced <strong>physics simulation</strong> where every block behaves naturally.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a world</strong> of adventure and rescue your friends!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 70 levels of mayhem and destruction.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TNT, confetti and fireworks for more spectacular explosions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steamworks</strong> integration to share and play creations from other players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Creator Mode</strong> where you can build your own levels!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blow it up is the ultimate explosive experience!!</p>",
